window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Celebrate the New Year the monstrous way with this holiday hockey monster romance!</b></p> <p>One hot chocolate crisis at a holiday dinner party, an unforgettable mistletoe kiss, and suddenly, I'm falling for one of the hottest goalies in the NMHL.</p> <p>Ehrokk is a sweet orc with hard muscles, a soft heart, and the kind of submissive eyes that draw me right in. As a vampire, I've been alive for centuries, but there's something about him that calls to me.</p> <p>After a New Year's Eve that changes us both, we wonder if we're fated to be together. But we lead such different lives that we aren't sure we can make it work. Can we give true love a shot?</p> <p><i>What you'll find in this novella: M/M monster romance, a silver-fox Vampire chef, a sweet Orc hockey player, D/s dynamics, champagne flavoredâ€¦ you know what, and knotty and naughty times.</i></p>"; 
